prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, clinging upside-down to a single, sturdy party balloon that is slowly floating upwards. The sloth has a comically lazy, blissful expression. Below the sloth, a single, beautifully wrapped gift with a ribbon has just slipped from its grasp and is beginning to fall. The background is a clean, minimalist wash of soft pastel blues and greens. In the center, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire image is in a delightful watercolor painting style, with soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges. Flat 2D artwork.
